README for trinity-gtk-theme


CONFIGURATION
=============

  GTK-2.0
  -------

  Create ~/.gtkrc-2.0 with approximately the following content:

    gtk-theme-name="Trinity"
    gtk-icon-theme-name="Trinity"
    gtk-font-name="Terminus (TTF) Medium 9"
    gtk-cursor-theme-name="Trinity-Cursor-Theme"
    gtk-cursor-theme-size=0
    gtk-toolbar-style=GTK_TOOLBAR_BOTH
    gtk-toolbar-icon-size=GTK_ICON_SIZE_SMALL_TOOLBAR
    gtk-button-images=1
    gtk-menu-images=1
    gtk-enable-event-sounds=1
    gtk-enable-input-feedback-sounds=1
    gtk-xft-antialias=0
    gtk-xft-hinting=0
    gtk-xft-hintstyle="none"
    gtk-xft-rgba="none"

  GTK-3.0
  -------

  Create ~/.config/gtk-3.0/settings.ini with approximately the
  following content:

    [Settings]
    gtk-theme-name=Trinity
    gtk-icon-theme-name=Trinity
    gtk-font-name=Terminus (TTF) Medium 9
    gtk-cursor-theme-size=0
    gtk-toolbar-style=GTK_TOOLBAR_BOTH
    gtk-toolbar-icon-size=GTK_ICON_SIZE_SMALL_TOOLBAR
    gtk-button-images=1
    gtk-menu-images=1
    gtk-enable-event-sounds=1
    gtk-enable-input-feedback-sounds=1
    gtk-xft-antialias=0
    gtk-xft-hinting=0
    gtk-xft-hintstyle=none
    gtk-xft-rgba=none
    gtk-cursor-theme-name=Trinity-Cursor-Theme


End of file.
